{
  "stem": "18258.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we followed the newspapers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew-- I would like to backtrack and just mention the one thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In 1921, we had, in Vienna, hunger riots in the center of the city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All of a sudden, they were rioting, looting food stores.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we got word of it, we closed our store, rolled the shutters down, and that afternoon we sent the women workers home.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that afternoon, we just-- we were closed up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But that was, as far as I remember, just one afternoon, hunger riots in Vienna, 1921.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they were not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We read the newspapers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we didn't know too much about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Those things really started affecting us in 1927.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When they had the process in-- the politically processing Vienna, when two right-wingers got acquitted for murder which had occurred early in spring.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the easternmost province, in Burgenland, there was a demonstration. two of the-- the labor people who had been there had been assassinated.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were brought to court in Vienna in '27, July 15, 1927, they were acquitted and the organized labor in Vienna marched from the outlying districts from the various factories where there was, of course, always groups organized, union groups, and marched into the city.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it ended up with Justizpalast [? in ?] [? those ?] [? days ?] the main Superior Court building in Vienna, Justizpalast.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I happened to be, at that time already, a member of the Academic [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Schutzbund. ?] And that morning, I was on a delivery trip for my dad's company to a company in the city.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we passed over the square where the Justizpalast was standing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we saw already the masses of union groups there and the first fist fights and arguments with the police.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
